OL,6,FHe then stole a flat screen
OL,7,Ftelevision, a tablet, several
OL,8,Fsuitcases, distinctive bottles of
OL,9,Falcohol and jewellery including
OL,10,Fdiamond rings, diamond earrings,
OL,11,Fbroaches, pendants, pearl chains, a
OL,12,Fruby ring and Georgian drop diamond
OL,13,Fearrings.
OL,15,FWhen the victim returned to her home
OL,16,Fthe following day, she found her home
OL,17,Fhad been broken in to and all her
OL,18,Fpersonal items stolen.
