OL,6,F"I just felt so vulnerable living
OL,7,Falone and the nights after the
OL,8,Fburglary were very uncomfortable for
OL,9,Fme, up until I knew he had been
OL,10,Fcaught. I would hear every noise and
OL,11,Fwake up worried that he had returned.
OL,13,F"To have that feeling of being scared
OL,14,Fin your own house is horrible. He not
OL,15,Fonly took my property but he took away
OL,16,Fmy sense of security in my own home.
